author: Connor Creates
description:
I was pretty darn nervous to start making videos and pursuing my creative ideas. But so glad I did it! An incredible past 2 years of having the blessing to do what I love and I feel like this is still only the beginning! 

I’m so grateful to everyone who watches and supports my videos, legit I think we’ve got the best YT community ever!
title: My Past 2 Years on YouTube
